================================================================================

MSCOCO T2I Model Weights
------------------------

The MSCOCO T2I model weights (mscoco-t2i-128 adapter) are from:
https://github.com/PeterWang512/AttributeByUnlearning

Licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.

Citation:
    @inproceedings{wang2024attributebyunlearning,
        title={Attributing Learned Concepts in Neural Networks to Training Data},
        author={Wang, Sheng-Yu and Adebara, Iyanuoluwa and Leino, Klas and
                Fredrikson, Matt and Zhu, Jun-Yan},
        booktitle={NeurIPS},
        year={2024}
    }

The model architecture uses diffusers' UNet2DConditionModel (Apache 2.0).

