U-Net Architecture
------------------

The U-Net architecture was originally proposed by:

    Ronneberger, O., Fischer, P., Brox, T. (2015). U-Net: Convolutional
    Networks for Biomedical Image Segmentation. Medical Image Computing and
    Computer-Assisted Intervention (MICCAI), LNCS 9351, 234-241.

    arXiv:1505.04597

The diffusion model adapters in this package use U-Net-based architectures
as implemented in the respective model codebases.
